" EasyMotion
nmap s <ESC>
nmap n <ESC>

" Multiple Indent
vmap >> >><ESC>gv
vmap << <<<ESC>gv

" Disable some useless functions.
" * Shift-Arrow actions
noremap <S-Up> <Up>
noremap <S-Down> <Down>
noremap <S-Left> <Left>
noremap <S-Right> <Right>
inoremap <S-Up> <Up>
inoremap <S-Down> <Down>
inoremap <S-Left> <Left>
inoremap <S-Right> <Right>
